snippet.title: First Contact | "The Wendigo" SCP-323
snippet.description:
Witness the first-ever recorded encounter in the wild with SCP-323 and uncover how this relentless enemy that will be stalking you throughout the game ended up being sent to Site-113. 
Follow our Kickstarter: https://bit.ly/3qCk8dI 

Huge thanks to ForlornFoundry for putting this amazing environment together, doing the editing and animations! Support his SCP-999 Plushie Kickstarter here: https://bit.ly/3mKi0zB

Wishlist us on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1184790/SCP_Fragmented_Minds/ 

Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/3eBHnru 



#SCP #indie #animation #SCPFoundation #wendigo #horror
